OL,3,CReport reveals '130 red flag
OL,4,Cincidents' involving schoolboy killer
OL,6,FThe family of murdered teenager Harvey
OL,7,FWillgoose says a new report documents
OL,8,F130 "red flag" incidents involving his
OL,9,Fkiller at a previous school.
OL,11,FMohammed Umar Khan was 15 when he
OL,12,Fstabbed Harvey, who was also 15, at
OL,13,FAll Saints Catholic High School in
OL,14,FSheffield a year ago.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,17,F16-year term last October.
