OL,6,FAn external investigation into the
OL,7,Fincident, commissioned by St Clare
OL,8,FCatholic MultiAcademy Trust, which
OL,9,Fruns the school, has now finished.
OL,11,FIts findings have not been published.
OL,13,FBut lawyers for Harvey's family, who
OL,14,Fhave seen the report, say it
OL,15,Fhighlights "missed opportunities" to
OL,16,Faddress Khan's behaviour before the
