OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference,
OL,7,FHarvey's grandmother Maria Turner said
OL,8,Fthere were multiple "red flags that
OL,9,Fwere missed".
OL,11,F"One flag in particular stood out,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"Umar's school record from Silverdale
OL,15,F(School) had 130 incidents including
OL,16,Fviolence, gangs, weapons and anger and
OL,17,Fthe school didn't pick up on this -
OL,18,Fand if they did it was too late."
