OL,6,FKhan had been transferred from
OL,7,FSilverdale to All Saints months before
OL,8,Fhe stabbed Harvey twice with a hunting
OL,9,Fknife during a lunch break. Harvey
OL,10,Fdied at the scene.
OL,12,FThe jury at Khan's trial was told how
OL,13,Fthe two boys had no history of
OL,14,Fhostility but had fallen out on social
OL,15,Fmedia following an incident in the
OL,16,Fschool involving two other pupils five
OL,17,Fdays before the stabbing.
OL,19,FCCTV shown during the trial showed
OL,20,FKhan shoving Harvey in a corridor on
OL,21,Fthe morning of the killing.
