OL,6,FThe jury heard he had an "unhealthy"
OL,7,Finterest in weapons. Images and video
OL,8,Ffound on his phone captured him posing
OL,9,Fwith knives and other weapons.
OL,11,FLaw firm Irwin Mitchell said an
OL,12,Finvestigation - carried out by a
OL,13,Fformer headteacher and inspector of
OL,14,Fschools - found that school leaders
OL,15,F"could, and at times should, have
OL,16,Ftaken different action" and were
OL,17,Fguilty of "oversights, assumptions and
OL,18,Fmisjudgements".
