OL,6,FIt said the report identified
OL,7,Fweaknesses in leadership, gaps in
OL,8,Fpolicy, poor implementation of
OL,9,Fgovernment guidance and serious
OL,10,Fshortcomings in recordkeeping that
OL,11,Fmeant weaponsrelated concerns and
OL,12,Fworrying behaviours were not acted
OL,13,Fupon effectively.
OL,15,FYogi Amin, head of public law and
OL,16,Fhuman rights at Irwin Mitchell, said
OL,17,Fthe report showed safeguarding and
OL,18,Fbehaviour records were not requested
OL,19,For reviewed before Khan's move from
