OL,6,FHis mother Caroline Willgoose said:
OL,7,F"Harvey was the light of our lives.
OL,8,FAnyone who knew him will tell you he
OL,9,Fwas a funloving, cheeky, sociable kid
OL,10,Fwho filled every room with energy. He
OL,11,Fhad big dreams, he was always
OL,12,Flaughing, always bringing people
OL,13,Ftogether. Losing him has torn a hole
OL,14,Fin our family that will never be
OL,15,Frepaired.
