OL,6,F"Every day since Harvey was taken from
OL,7,Fus has been agony. I still hear his
OL,8,Fvoice saying 'I love you' before he
OL,9,Fleft for school that morning ` the
OL,10,Flast words he ever said to me. No
OL,11,Fparent should outlive their child, and
OL,12,Fcertainly not because of something as
OL,13,Fsenseless and avoidable as a knife
OL,14,Fbeing brought into school.
