OL,6,F"Reading the findings of this report
OL,7,Fhas been devastating. To see in black
OL,8,Fand white the chances there were to
OL,9,Fstep in, the signs that were missed
OL,10,Fand how many opportunities there were
OL,11,Fto protect my boy is something I'll
OL,12,Fcarry with me for the rest of my life.
OL,13,FHarvey deserved better. All the
OL,14,Fchildren in that school deserved
OL,15,Fbetter.
OL,17,F"We'll always be angry by what
OL,18,Fhappened to Harvey but more than
OL,19,Fanything I'm determined to unite
OL,20,Fpeople to bring about change for the
OL,21,Fbetter."
